=top align=left class=m><span class=title> How's thread drop rate now?</span><hr size=1> Ive fought this zone both pre and post patch and I've NEVER seen a thread drop... my bad luck? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarantrunemaster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arant Runemaster</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://verbalsabre.50megs.com/images/cooked.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/5/01 6:20:18 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How's thread drop rate now?</span><hr size=1> test <p><img src="http://members.tripod.com/~nuke4u2/soup.gif"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uxandargnome.showPublicProfile?language=EN>xandar gnome</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/5/01 7:46:21 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.xandar.net/gareese/eq_pictures/september/new_robe.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How's thread drop rate now?</span><hr size=1> I spent about 6 - 7 hours in Velks yesterday, and got about 80 threads in that time.  It was my first time fighting spiders in that zone, so don't now if that was more than usual or not.  Every 12th spider or so would drop threads it seemed like. <p>~Xandar~
