tchers and devourers drop 3-5 threads each. We only pulled one hunter, we were mainly working the floor and lower ramps (warrior was pulling, no point half killing him jumping off the ramps). A few hours soloing boring green wurms and looking for ones that glow, and I got the biles. If I don't muff the combine, I would say a total of about 15 hours spent gathering stuff for this shawl.<br>
